  "text": "State the point at which an individualized entity of second density is ready for a transition to third. Is this second density being what we would call animal. I am Ra. There are three types of second density entities which become, shall we say, an spirited. The first is the animal. This is the most predominant. The second is the vegetable, most especially that which you call sound vibration, complex, tree. These entities are capable of giving and receiving enough love to become individualized. The third category is a mineral occasionali, a certain location, a place as you may call it, becomes energized to individuality through the love it receives and gives in relationship to a third density entity which is in relationship to it. This is the least common transition.",
